            <h2>Setup Instructions</h2>
            <ol>
                <li>Clone the repo: <code>git clone https://github.com/&lt;your-username&gt;/v2-accelerators.git</code></li>
                <li>Navigate: <code>cd v2-accelerators/accelerators</code></li>
                <li>Deploy infrastructure (Terraform/CloudFormation): <code>terraform init && terraform apply</code></li>
                <li>Configure AWS CLI credentials in <code>~/.aws/credentials</code>.</li>
                <li>Run <code>python3 scripts/analyze_costs.py</code> to generate the first cost report.</li>
            </ol>
